snippet.title: Baseball Stars 2 Gameplay PS3
snippet.description: Available for purchase in the playstation store.  Been a long time since I played the original game.  Glad to see that they brought it to the PS3.  A fast paced arcade style baseball game.   Let me know if you guys would want me to upload a full game.
